Bugday is [[Article description::a single day each month devoted to improving Gentoo in all aspects.]]

<big>'''Next Bugday:''' <mark>July 1st, 2017</mark></big>

'''Who:''' Gentoo Community (developers and users) - organized by the Gentoo Bugday team.

'''When:''' Usually on the first '''Saturday''' of every month, when possible. <!-- '''When:''' Every '''first Saturday''' of every month -->

'''Time:''' 24h event.

'''Where:''' The [irc://irc.freenode.net/gentoo-bugs #gentoo-bugs] channel on Freenode IRC.

== Requirements==

# A Gentoo installation.
# An IRC client.
# A Gentoo Bugzilla account.
# Wiki account (optional).
# Good mood and a friendly attitude.

== Tasks ==

# Fix bugs.
# Bug triaging.
# Version bumps.
# Close old fixed bugs.
# Add or improve documentation here on the wiki.

